  <p class="sub">A systems sketch with one named feedback. The link, not the drawing, is the point.</p>
  <div class="submission-callout">
    <div class="label">📥 Systems sketch + one feedback</div>
    <p>Two things: (1) a sketch of the five urban systems for your area, and (2) one named feedback between two of them, stated as a mechanism ("more paving for density removes permeable land, which lowers flood resilience"), plus a sentence on what it means for design. A label with no mechanism ("density affects flooding") does not clear the bar.</p>
